{"tid":2072572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★橫濱等身大可動高達開始外殼組裝","createTime":"2020-06-20T16:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T04:58:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8f6d536a4cd63c4d9e070e38e13d08479a5c99d2","tid":2072572,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Ea73UkJUMAIYnOm-694x461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2FEa73UkJUMAIYnOm-694x461.jpg&h=6c264527&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n名為「Gundam Global Challenge」的計劃旨在召集世界各地的機械和設計技術，實現可動式等身大高達的製作。而這個計劃已經進入最後階段，原先計劃在 2020 年 10 月於日本橫濱山下碼頭開放，不過就因爲武漢肺炎疫情而宣佈延期，目前還未有確實的開放日期。雖然如此，計劃本身則繼續進行中，最近有日本網民就發現高達已經開始外殼組裝，肩甲和手部裝甲都陸續安裝完成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/06/20/action-gundam-life-size/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F20%2Faction-gundam-life-size%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduXjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=670fd642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/06/20/action-gundam-life-size/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"f739d27e8412bc8a675aeedba582d8ced6ae2935","tid":2072572,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/Ea73UgwUMAICtM6-694x461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2FEa73UgwUMAICtM6-694x461.jpg&h=14cc101d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2adc23824f4d735a9154e67a3418992a37f87f8","tid":2072572,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"大日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=